    description: 'Optimized database queries and implemented caching strategies in a JavaScript/TypeScript environment, reducing API response times by 40%. And also, collaborated as Backend in more than 3 proyects',
  },
  {
    date: '2024',
    title: 'Backend Developer Freelance',
